Date of Birth: January 31, 1872<br/>
Birthplace: Daloe, Trondhjem, Norway<br/>
Ordained apostle: March 17, 1921<br/>
Death: November 29, 1952<br/>
<br/>
Born Jan. 31, 1872, at Daloe, Island of Froyen, Trondhjem, Norway, to John A. Widtsoe and Anna Karine Gaarden.
Ordained apostle March 17, 1921, by Heber J. Grant, at age 49; died Nov. 29, 1952, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 80.